                   person("Stephan", "Rosenzweig")),
  year         = "2023",
  url          = "https://hydflood.bafg.de/index.html",
  textVersion  =
  paste0("Weber, A., & Rosenzweig, S. (2023): hydflood - Flood Extents and Dur",
         "ations along the Rivers Elbe and Rhine. URL https://hydflood.bafg.de",
         "/index.html.")
)
